text.tspan: UK: Number of COVID-19 patients in hospital
Hospitalization data is available for individual UK nations, and English data by NHS Region. Data from the four
nations may not be directly comparable as data about COVID-19 patients in hospitals are collected differently.
Data source: Government of the United Kingdom (2024)
